Encapsulation kya hai

"Apni data aur functions ko ek unit (class) ke andar chhupa kar rakhna, aur baahir ke code ko direct access na dena."
	Data ko direct access nahi hota, sirf method se hota hai
    Aap decide karte hain kaunsa data bahar jaaye ya nahi
    Code easy hota hai maintain karna

    Encapsulation = Data ko private banana + access ke liye getter/setter dena

    Real-life Example: Bank Account System
    Aap ek banking app bana rahe hain. Har user ka ek account balance hota hai â€” lekin kya kisi bhi user ko directly balance change karne denge?

Nahi!
Balance chhupa kar (private) rakhna hoga, aur sirf deposit() aur withdraw() method se access milega.